document_name: Strengthening Innovative Partnerships for Development Cooperation (SIP-DC)

outputs.output_descr: BAPPENAS and related line ministries capacity to establish and foster global partnership for development cooperation strengthened

project_descr: Strengthening Innovative Partnerships for Development Cooperation (SIP-DC). The project will support the Government of Indonesia  (GoI) in moving forward from the paradigm of donor-recipient relationships to partnerships for development effectiveness.
